Infused with calendula and sunflower seed oils, it hydrates and soothes while adding radiance. No cakey finish, no clogged pores just a buttery smooth glow that looks like real, healthy skin.

I use it on my cheekbones, nose tips, inner corners, and even lips. It’s versatile, skincare-packed, and fits that clean girl vibe perfectly. Also Made in Korea!
